  • Constructor Details

    • Boost

      public Boost(double x, double y, double width, double height)
      Constructs a Boost object with the specified position, dimensions, and an image file. The size of the boost is adjusted based on the provided width and height.
      Parameters:
      x - The x-coordinate of the boost's position.
      y - The y-coordinate of the boost's position.
      width - The width of the boost (scaled for the image).
      height - The height of the boost (scaled for the image).
